# .DEV.TODO — vaked-oracle roadmap

Backlog for the LLM-assisted reverse-engineering subsystem (`tools/oracle/`).
Slice 1 SHIPPED (origin/main `5308672`): ralph-loop → PyGhidra → llm4decompile-6.7B
refine → fidelity-vs-FOSS → Frida+eBPF dynamic evidence → finding + hash-chained
ledger + (unwired) kernel bridge. Acceptance proven on dev-cx53 (static + dynamic).

Premise: a decompiler-LLM reverse-engineers the runtime of another LLM
(llama.cpp / libllama.so.0). FOSS target ⇒ objective fidelity. Recursive.

