## BACKLOG (user: "don't forget the others")

### Slice 3 — agentic reverser → PROMOTED to active (see top). Chosen: hybrid
LLM-driven policy + crabcc-powered investigate. Off-the-shelf free-form agent CLIs
(claude/pi/nullclaw) deferred — the auditable LLM-policy middle ground won.

### Slice 4 — arbitrary-binary RE  (generality)
Unknown/stripped ELFs — the pure llm4decompile / OGhidra demo. Proves the system
works beyond the FOSS-ground-truth case. No ground truth ⇒ needs a confidence
heuristic to replace fidelity-vs-source scoring (self-consistency / recompile-diff).

### Slice 5 — deepen target + fidelity  (hardening)
- ggml/tensor hot path: `ggml_compute_forward`, `ggml_graph_compute` on
  `libggml-base.so` (more llama.cpp surface for static+dynamic acceptance).
- tree-sitter AST fidelity replacing `normalized-token-similarity` in `fidelity.py`.
- widen the eBPF watcher trace window to catch GGUF mmap.

